column5: Sugarpacket carved a special pumpkin for the season (bass season that is)!    Remember - Halloween means one month left of bassin! (in Southern Ontario anyway)  Happy halloween!
She did an excellent job Rich!!!  Thanks for that one!
Did she use a template?  That's awesome!  cheers
Very cool pumpkin!  Kudos to Sugarpacket!
Great job SP was that done with the fillet Knife lol
That is real awesome...... great carving SP Leechman
Very cool.  Hope the little one enjoys Halloween.
thats a wicked pumpkin carving! i have seen some crazy stuff people do. Wish i had talent like that ha.
All that talent and she fishes. What a catch. Your a lucky guy Rich. (Just in case she sees this you should probably make the obligatory reply that, yes you are)
Nice fish pumpkin! Hope your child has a great time tonite. My kid like this day second to Christmas.
